name: Squad Wars
blurb: Take control of a state of the art spacefighter in SQUAD WARS\u2122, the new team based space combat game built by END Games Entertainment.

rewards.reward: Every dollar counts in the quest for putting our dreams into tangible form. Thank you so much!
- Exclusive wallpaper featuring one of your favourite ship designs.\r\n - Your name listed as a Kickstarter on our official development blog.
RECRUIT LEVEL gets you: access to the Beta; a Founder's Recruit In-Game Badge, $20 worth of in game credits at launch; you get 1 vote on deciding our first scenario; and our sincere appreciation!

STICK JOCKEY LEVEL gets you: Beta access; a Founder's Stick Jockey In-Game Badge; one month of free XP boost; 1 day headstart at launch; a total of 2 first scenario votes; and a total of $50 worth of in game credits at launch

FLYBOY LEVEL gets you: Beta access; a Founder's Flyboy In-Game Badge; three months of free XP boost; 1 day headstart at launch; Early registration to reserve your callsign; Access to behind the scene development forums; a total of 5 first scenario votes; a total of $100 worth of in game credits at launch; and a "Special Thanks" development credit

ACE LEVEL gets you: game access during Alpha stages; a Founder's Ace In-Game Badge; permanent XP boost; 2 day headstart at launch; Early callsign registration; Access to VIP development forums; Special limited edition ship paint jobs; a total of 10 first scenario votes; a total of $225 worth of in game credits; and a "Founder" development credit

WING COMMANDER LEVEL gets you Ace level rewards PLUS: a Founder's Wing Commander In-Game Badge;  Early squad name registration; A poster autographed by the development team; a total of 25 first scenario votes; a total of $600 worth of in game credits; and a "Backer" development credit

CAPTAIN LEVEL gets you Wing Commander level rewards PLUS: a Founder's Captain In-Game Badge; An autographed piece of original concept art; An art book showcasing visuals and design concepts; a total of 50 first scenario votes;a total of $1200 worth of in game credits; and a "Patron" development credit

ADMIRAL LEVEL gets you Captain level rewards PLUS: a Founder's Admiral In-Game Badge; You name an item or ship in the game; Custom designed squad graphic: our artists will create your squad's logo to your specifications (within game limitations); An exclusive launch party invite (must be able to travel to event venue on your own); a total of 100 first scenario votes;a total of $2500 worth of in game credits; a Squad Council seat, giving you 1 VIP vote on influencing future content and feature directions; and an "Associate Producer" development credit

LEGEND LEVEL gets you Admiral level rewards PLUS: a Founder's Legend In-Game Badge for you; an exclusive Legendary In-Game Badge for your entire squad; You name a sector in the game; a VIP invite to the launch party (must be able to travel to event venue on your own); a total of 500 first scenario votes;a total of $13,000 worth of in game credits; five Squad Council seats, giving you 5 VIP votes on influencing future content and feature directions;  a "Co-Producer" development credit

SPACE DEITY LEVEL gets you Legend level rewards PLUS: a Founder's Space Deity In-Game Badge; Your character is written into game lore; 2 VIP invites to the launch party and 1 night hotel stay (must be able to travel to event venue on your own); A private, tasty lunch or dinner with END Games studio heads; a total of 1000 first scenario votes;a total of $25,000 worth of in game credits; ten Squad Council seats, giving you 10 VIP votes on influencing future content and feature directions;  a "Co-Executive Producer" development credit

Gets you Legend Level rewards PLUS: Your permanent ad displayed in the map of your choosing as a floating billboard. You supply the ad (so long as it meets the games rating and technical requirements) and we run it. You can change it whenever you would like as well. It will be part of the game for as long as the game is live.
